ia - Treaty of Paris 1259","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"When Grace Hungerford was born in 1225, in Stourton, Wiltshire, England, her father, Sir Walter de Hungerford, was 40 and her mother, Countess Hawise de Quincy, was 41. She married Eudes de Stourton in 1251, in Willey, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1261, in her hometown, at the age of 36, and was buried in Stourton, Wiltshire, England."},"et":{"1225–1261":"1225–1261","1230–1281":"1230–1281","1220–1285":"1220–1285","1230–1265":"1230–1265","1251–1303":"1251–1303","1245–1331":"1245–1331","1185–Male":"1185–Surnud","1184–1263":"1184–1263","1220":"1220","1263":"1263","1285":"1285","1230":"1230","1251":"1251","1185":"1185","1261":"1261","1184":"1184","1281":"1281","Abt 1251":"umbes 1251","1259":"1259","1303":"1303","1225":"1225","Abt 1245":"umbes 1245","1245":"1245","1331":"1331","1265":"1265","Wiltshire, England":"Wiltshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Stourton, Wiltshire, England":"Stourton, Wiltshire, England","Willey, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Willey, Shropshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Probably Willey, Salop, Shropshire, England":"Willey, Shropshire, England"},"fi":{"1225–1261":"1225–1261","1230–1281":"1230–1281","1220–1285":"1220–1285","1230–1265":"1230–1265","1251–1303":"1251–1303","1245–1331":"1245–1331","1185–Male":"1185–Kuollut","1184–1263":"1184–1263","1220":"1220","1263":"1263","1285":"1285","1230":"1230","1251":"1251","1185":"1185","1261":"1261","1184":"1184","1281":"1281","Abt 1251":"noin 1251","1259":"1259","1303":"1303","1225":"1225","Abt 1245":"noin 1245","1245":"1245","1331":"1331","1265":"1265","Wiltshire, England":"Wiltshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Stourton, Wiltshire, England":"Stourton, Wiltshire, England","Willey, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Willey, Shropshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Probably Willey, Salop, Shropshire, England":"Willey, Shropshire, England"},"fr":{"1225–126